    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and honestly, it's been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years\u2014perfect for someone who wants a smooth, dependable ride without the brand-new price tag. It runs beautifully and is just waiting for someone to take it on its next big adventure. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
