    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit exhibits crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and pulls strongly through the entire powerband to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement with precise gate entry. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The M Variable Differential Lock remains tight, providing excellent exit traction. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with a well-enjoyed driver\u2019s car, the chassis dynamics and powertrain performance remain sharp. A purist-spec example ready for the B-roads.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Minor cosmetic wear. Runs well. Title in hand.",
