    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been exceptionally well-maintained and serves as a prime example of its model. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, though closer inspection reveals a few minor stone chips consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with supple leather upholstery that has been regularly conditioned; all power features, including the dual-zone climate control and premium sound system, function perfectly. Mechanically, it is robust, having followed a strict maintenance schedule with recent service including a fresh oil change and a new set of high-performance tires. It drives straight and true, with smooth gear transitions and responsive braking. A complete service history and two sets of keys are included. This is a reliable, turnkey vehicle ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
