    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It still runs like a dream and looks great parked in the driveway! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Perfect for your daily commute or weekend adventures\u2014come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
