      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E92 M3, a definitive peak for the naturally aspirated S65 V8. This 4.0L unit features individual throttle bodies and a cross-plane crank, delivering a linear power delivery optimized for its 8,400 RPM redline. The 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission provides instantaneous gear synchronization and crisp rev-matching. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a variable M differential lock, ensuring exceptional lateral grip and corner-exit traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and new throttle actuators, addressing key S65 weak points. The hydraulic steering rack remains precise, offering the communicative feedback essential for spirited driving. A well-maintained enthusiast spec with a focus on drivetrain performance.",
